title: [ArborSong, Cell]
description: Isolation and desolation seem to be the theme here.  The flimsy cot holds a fur that might once have been a blanket, while ominous stains darken the floor beneath the embedded iron rings, often trailing outside the cell to a chipped basin near a fallen broom in the corner.  Only the cell door appears untouched by decay.
room.location: Arborsong, inside the island town of Mist Harbor
